{
"#name"
:
{
"claw"
:
null
,
"cn"
:
"x-cmd AI 消息机器人"
,
"en"
:
"x-cmd AI message bot"
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
{
"x claw <SUBCMD>"
:
null
}
]
,
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"自托管 AI Agent 网关，将 LLM 接入微信、飞书、Telegram 等即时通讯平台。\n监听 IM 消息并触发本地 AI Agent 执行自主任务，支持通过 `x agent request` 调用\nclaude, codex, cursor, gemini-cli, opencode, kimi-cli 等多种 AI 引擎，\n每个会话拥有独立 workspace 与持久化上下文记忆。\n"
,
"en"
:
"A self-hosted AI Agent gateway that connects LLMs to WeChat, Feishu, Telegram and other IM platforms.\nListens for IM messages and triggers local AI Agents to execute autonomous tasks,\nsupporting multiple AI engines via `x agent request` (claude, codex, cursor, gemini-cli, opencode, kimi-cli),\nwith independent workspaces and persistent context memory per session.\n"
}
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"使用 'x claw run' 启动网关服务（默认微信）。\n支持的 IM 平台: weixin, telegram, feishu, qywx。\nAI Agent 引擎可通过 'x agent request' 配置切换（如 claude, codex, cursor, gemini-cli, opencode, kimi-cli）。\n"
,
"en"
:
"Use 'x claw run' to start the gateway (default: WeChat).\nSupported IM platforms: weixin, telegram, feishu, qywx.\nAI Agent engine can be switched via 'x agent request' config (e.g. claude, codex, cursor, gemini-cli, opencode, kimi-cli).\n"
}
]
,
"#subcmd:Service"
:
[
"run"
,
"service"
]
,
"#subcmd:inner"
:
[
"weixin"
,
"telegram"
,
"feishu"
,
"agentrequest"
]
,
"run"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"启动 AI Agent 消息网关，连接 IM 平台并实时监听、自动处理消息。"
,
"en"
:
"Launch the AI Agent message gateway to connect to an IM platform for real-time listening and autonomous message processing."
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
{
"x claw run [IM]"
:
null
}
]
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"即时通讯平台名称（默认 weixin）"
,
"en"
:
"IM platform name (default: weixin)"
}
,
"#cand"
:
[
"weixin"
,
"telegram"
,
"feishu"
,
"qywx"
]
}
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"该命令在前台运行，保持终端打开以持续监听消息。如需后台运行，请配合 screen/tmux 或使用 service 命令。\n启动前请确保已配置对应的 IM 平台服务（如 `x weixin login`）。\n新消息到达时自动分派到独立 worker 处理。\nAI Agent 回复引擎由 `x agent request` 决定，支持 claude, codex, cursor, gemini-cli, opencode, kimi-cli 等。\n内置心跳机制与 x cron 集成，支持定时唤醒和 proactive 任务执行。\n每个 chat 拥有独立 workspace 与持久化上下文记忆，支持多会话并发。\n"
,
"en"
:
"This command runs in the foreground; keep the terminal open to continue listening. Use screen/tmux or the service command for background execution.\nEnsure the corresponding IM platform service is configured before starting (e.g. `x weixin login`).\nDispatches incoming messages to independent workers for processing.\nThe AI Agent reply engine is determined by `x agent request`, supporting claude, codex, cursor, gemini-cli, opencode, kimi-cli, etc.\nBuilt-in heartbeat mechanism with x cron integration supports scheduled wake-ups and proactive task execution.\nEach chat has an independent workspace with persistent context memory, supporting multi-session concurrency.\n"
}
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x claw run"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 启动微信网关服务"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Start the WeChat gateway"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x claw run telegram"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 启动 Telegram 网关服务"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Start the Telegram gateway"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x claw run feishu"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 启动飞书网关服务"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Start the Feishu gateway"
}
]
}
,
"service"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"后台托管 x claw run 服务（start/stop/status/log）"
,
"en"
:
"Run x claw run as a background managed gateway (start/stop/status/log)"
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x claw service start telegram"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 启动 Telegram 网关服务"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Start the Telegram gateway"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x claw service stop telegram"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 停止 Telegram 网关服务"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Stop the Telegram gateway"
}
]
,
"start"
:
{
